lead_paragraph: Ross Taylor and Kane Williamson scored centuries as New Zealand posted a massive 582 for four declared in their first innings against Zimbabwe on the second day of the second test on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Taylor, Williamson Centuries Boost New Zealand to Massive Total
